# Graphify knowledge graph
# We use the gsd graphify command, which reads/writes .planning/graphs/.
# graph.json + GRAPH_REPORT.md + graph.html are committed so graphify runs on clone.
# Regenerable diff cache (rebuilt by `/gsd:graphify build`):
.planning/graphs/.last-build-snapshot.json
# Standalone graphify CLI output — unused; gsd graphify is canonical:
graphify-out/
